name: LocalizedDystoniaOfExtremitiesICD10CM
title: Localized Dystonia of Extremities (ICD10CM)
description: This value set includes ICD10CM concepts for localized dystonia of extremities.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set includes ICD10CM concepts for localized dystonia of extremities.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify people diagnosed with localized dystonia of extremities. This element may map to "Diagnosis" Category of the Quality Data Model.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes localized or segmental dystonia. Includes dystonia of upper and lower extremities.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes generalized dystonia. Excludes dystonia of regions of the body other than upper and lower extremities.)
